data.description: Occupancy Passed  - If LOCATION is important - STOP! This is it!! Minutes away from Grants Farm, Grants trail and every amenity you could need - Gyms, Grocery stores, Restaurants including Sam's Steakhouse. You'll be saying Yes when you pull up to this Solid Brick Ranch home. Gorgeous, original hardwood floors on main level. Spacious living room with picture window, separate dining room and eat-in kitchen. Updated electric, newer high efficiency HVAC, newer windows &  6 panel doors. New roof 2023 with new oversized gutter & gutter guards, 2 car attached garage with newer garage door. The wide 3 car driveway is a show stopper. Finished basement with bonus room to be used for office/sleeping, etc. New basement flooring, Fenced backyard with French drain.  Must see before it is gone !!!!!!
